  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 00c9c9bb92b3b44fb84ca335c48467d8, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue_Act4_Aldric_Offer
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Hollowfen.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _id: act4.aldric.offer
  _lines:
  - speaker: Wren
    text: The candle was low when I finally spread the letter open on the table.
      Lord Aldric wrote beautifully. That was the first danger.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c35722ef4d86047169515e86f6d556c1, type: 3}
  - speaker: Aldric's letter
    text: 'I had presumed, speaking honestly, that Hollowfen was finished.


      You
      have made that presumption incorrect, Miss Tobin.'
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fb47a9c51f5d349dc811d1b942bbdfcc, type: 3}
  - speaker: Aldric's letter
    text: I propose patronage, tax relief, and lawful protection under my banner.
    isCloseup: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c07320fcd0ec04f438f87250acfac8d9, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: The terms were generous. I read them once as myself, once as my father's
      daughter, and once as if my grandmother sat across the table with flour on
      her sleeve and opinions in her eyebrows. On the third reading, I found the
      hook.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 28b782e8f13a6420aaf577b870ab91de, type: 3}
  - speaker: Aldric's letter
    text: All cultivation records, wild-harvest routes, medicinal preparations, and
      trade rights shall be held in trust by my estate.
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 972dfe98b13cd4bc49047b2925f6f2ea, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: 'Held in trust.


      Owned, in prettier clothes.'
    isCloseup: 1
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 40ae6b3b44c98485aa52f92c22e4bd09, type: 3}
  - speaker: Wren
    text: I wondered how many villages had been saved into obedience before anyone
      thought to call it loss. Then I set the letter down, and began a list of who
      I needed to ask.
    isCloseup: 0
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8862a96f0584a4330ba403674d04eab2, type: 3}
